---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---
<MarketingLayout title="Privacy — Guardino Technologies" description="Our privacy practices: GDPR & KVKK compliant.">
  <article class="container-1078 privacy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Guardino Technologies LLC respects your privacy. This page is a placeholder for our full GDPR + KVKK compliant policy.</p>
    <h2>Data Controller</h2>
    <p>Guardino Technologies LLC, Istanbul / USA.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p><a href="mailto:privacy@guardinotechnologies.com">privacy@guardinotechnologies.com</a></p>
    <h2>Rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR (EU) and KVKK (Türkiye), you have rights to access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, and objection. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>
  </article>
</MarketingLayout>
<style>
  .privacy { padding: 96px 24px; max-width: 720px; }
  .privacy h1 { font-size: 39px; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .privacy h2 { font-size: 20px; margin: 32px 0 12px; font-weight: 600; }
  .privacy p { color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .privacy a { color: #a0e0ab; }
</style>
